  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "para_id": "Q001063.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) E-ana-tum , ruler of Lagaš , given strength by Enlil , nourished on rich milk by Ninhursaĝa , whose name was proclaimed by Ninĝirsu , chosen by Nanše in the heart , child of Aya-kurgal , ruler of Lagaš , defeated the highlands of Elam . He defeated Arawa . He defeated Umma . He defeated Urim ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001063.23",
      "line_range": "23",
      "translation": "(ii 12) At that time , he built a well of fired brick for Ninĝirsu in his courtyard and then Ninĝirsu was pleased by him , whose is personal god is Šul-MUŠxPA , by E-ana-tum ."
    }
  ],
